Dear C.Y.:

Thanks for your comments. I have combined your two responses and rearrang=
ed the
order of your comments in the responses below to avoid as much duplicatio=
n as
possible. However, to present a more or less logically ordered and
self-contained version for others not familiar (or confused) with our ear=
lier
discussions, I have quoted some earlier email paragraphs as well.

