       This is a binary tree for a Fedora Core 4 system. Unpack this tree in a directory such as /home::

         1) cd /home
         2) tar -zxf axiom-Sept2005-FC4-bin.tgz
         3) cd axiom
         4) export AXIOM=`pwd`/mnt/linux
         5) export PATH=\$AXIOM/bin:\$PATH
         6) axiom


